1. Problem Statement

Recruiters often receive thousands of resumes for a single job posting. Manual screening:
-Is time-consuming
-Introduces unconscious bias
-Misses strong candidates
-Does not scale

This system proposes a cloud-native, AI-powered resume screening platform that:
-Parses resumes
-Matches them semantically with job descriptions
-Ranks candidates
-Detects bias
-Provides explainable scoring
